Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺安定下來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我們龍騎兵被賦予的唯一使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人是不可能捕獲龍之轉矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個時候沒有被強制轉移的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經把那傢伙捕獲住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩還保持著自己的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不謹慎接觸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把那個捕獲住的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個拉庫利瑪需要龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹...幹什麼 紅秧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫利瑪會變成什麼樣 和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起活下去 小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣也很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有進展麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我收拾一下儲藏室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲藏室?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一個人是搬不起重物的 不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的12歲的暑假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為明年就要13歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這個暑假你應該盡情的做你喜歡想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼特別想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受兒提時代怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試結束以後 我會想怎麼玩就怎麼玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是攝影機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你出生的時候 爸爸買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還挺貴的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得哪裡不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的爸爸和媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在才辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚的時候花錢花的太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以媽媽決定不辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在才要舉辦儀式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羅曼蒂克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸媽媽直到現在感情還很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊 一直都是很恩愛的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是愛的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很適合禮服 在結婚式上大放異彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 一直都很溫柔而且漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是這樣 不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舉行儀式的真正的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...是愛的媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是高中生時候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好像不知道這事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好帥啊 愛的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不讓你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤 那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像專家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看上去是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑會用麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我說後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的結婚儀式 要不要來做攝影師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的媽媽和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到拍攝的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥啊 攝影師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在麼 內田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 五
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個團體都到齊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到試驗船這麼快就到達了
